  {
    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "1. It invents its own vocabulary mid-task and assumes you speak it.",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/godofprompt/status/2065501407181156450",
    "time": "2026-06-13 02:28",
    "created_at": "Fri Jun 12 18:28:05 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2065501407181156450",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "2. Don't let it write the code. Let it run the project.",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/godofprompt/status/2065501419390767596",
    "time": "2026-06-13 02:28",
    "created_at": "Fri Jun 12 18:28:08 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2065501419390767596",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "3. Three failure modes flagged: it collapses every topic into the narrowest frame, it litigates criticism instead of fixing the issue, and it mistakes rhetorical cleverness for rigor.",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/godofprompt/status/2065501431617245192",
    "time": "2026-06-13 02:28",
    "created_at": "Fri Jun 12 18:28:11 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2065501431617245192",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "4. One PR review burned nearly half a 5-hour budget to produce ONLY 3 real bugs, 5 minor polish notes, 2 scary false positives, and a pile of cleanup opinions.",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/godofprompt/status/2065501444112040068",
    "time": "2026-06-13 02:28",
    "created_at": "Fri Jun 12 18:28:14 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2065501444112040068",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "5. Flagged a cancer research question as a biology security risk.",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/godofprompt/status/2065501456795615534",
    "time": "2026-06-13 02:28",
    "created_at": "Fri Jun 12 18:28:17 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2065501456795615534",
    "is_retweet": false
